cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CC

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with hybrid logic and its complexity over linear orders and the natural numbers. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as hybrid logic is used in knowledge representation and reasoning in AI. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as hybrid logic has been used in some machine learning applications. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses the complexity of the satisfiability problem. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also a possibility as the paper deals with the complexity of the satisfiability problem in different fragments of hybrid logic.
